"Provides jQueryUI datepicker support for date and datetime elements. "
"jQueryUI is no longer maintained."
msgstr ""
"为日期和日期时间元素提供 jQueryUI "
"日期选择器（datepicker）支持。jQueryUI 已不再维护。"

