"Drush was unable to download the colorbox library from @remote. "
"@exception"
msgstr "Drush 无法从 @remote 下载 colorbox 库。@exception"

msgid "Error: unable to unzip colorbox file."
msgstr "错误：无法解压 colorbox 文件。"

