"Text or code that is placed directly in front of the input. This can "
"be used to prefix an input with a constant string. Examples: $, #, -."
msgstr "放置在输入框前面的文本或代码。可用于在输入前添加一个固定字符串作为前缀。示例：$、#、-。"

